ng trial]].<ref name="The Lawyer">{{cite news|title=Rebekah Brooks’ legal team revealed as gagging order lifted |url= https://www.thelawyer.com/issues/online-october-2013/rebekah-brooks-legal-team-revealed-as-gagging-order-lifted/ |accessdate=10 November 2017}}</ref> In 2012 he was chosen by the [[Football Association]] to present their case against [[John Terry]].<ref name="theguardian02">{{cite news|title=John Terry verdict: if the FA does not think this is racism, what is? |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2012/oct/05/john-terry-fa-commission |accessdate=10 November 2017}}</ref>
