The '''Navy Office of Information West''', also referred to as NAVINFO West, is a [[public affairs (military)|public affairs]] office in [[Los Angeles]] that serves as the primary Navy liaison to [[feature films]], [[documentary films]]  and [[television programs]] depicting or involving the [[US Navy]]. This office also maintains close relations and contacts in the [[entertainment industry]] with the goal of telling the US military's story by facilitating accurate information and relevant themes and messages.

